    <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:12.5pt;"><strong>CL&Aacute;USULA D&Eacute;CIMA PRIMEIRA</strong>:<span style="letter-spacing:-1.15pt;">&nbsp;</span>O<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>atraso<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>superior<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>30<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>(trinta)<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>dias<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>no<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>pagamento<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>da<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>parcela,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>facultar&aacute;<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>&agrave;<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span><strong><u>VENDEDORA</u></strong>,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>seu<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>crit&eacute;rio:</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:5.65pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:12.5pt;">I - Dar<span style="letter-spacing:-1.15pt;">&nbsp;</span>por<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>rescindido<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>o<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>contrato,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>aplicando-se<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>o<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>disposto<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>na<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>cl&aacute;usula<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>nona<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>deste<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>instrumento;</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:5.65pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:12.5pt;">II - Dar<span style="letter-spacing:-1.15pt;">&nbsp;</span>por<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>congelado<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>o<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>plano de compra,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>aguardando<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>assim<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>retomada<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>dos<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>pagamentos<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>ou<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>formaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>da<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>desist&ecirc;ncia;</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:5.65pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:12.5pt;">III - Dar<span style="letter-spacing:-1.15pt;">&nbsp;</span>por<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>rescindido<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>o<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>contrato,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>aplicando<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>cobran&ccedil;a<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>das<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>parcelas<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>em<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>atraso<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>e<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>vincendas,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>com<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>os<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>acr&eacute;scimos<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>legais;</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:12.5pt;"><strong>CL&Aacute;USULA D&Eacute;CIMA SEGUNDA</strong>: Como incentivo pelo pagamento pontual das parcelas, o <strong>COMPRADOR(A)&nbsp;</strong>participar&aacute; atrav&eacute;s do <span style="letter-spacing:-0.15pt;">sorteio&nbsp;</span>mensal<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>da<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>quita&ccedil;&atilde;o<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>integral<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>e<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>imediata<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>deste contrato,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>com<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>entrega<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>do<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>bem<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>ou<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>do<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>valor<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>objeto<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>deste contrato.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:12.5pt;"><strong>CL&Aacute;USULA D&Eacute;CIMA TERCEIRA</strong>: A participa&ccedil;&atilde;o no sorteio mensal ser&aacute; assegurada a todos os <strong><u>COMPRADORES(A)</u></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>adimplentes, como incentivo a pontualidade,<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span>com<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span>exclus&atilde;o<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>dos<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span>inadimplentes.<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>Desta<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span>forma<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span>o<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span><strong><u>COMPRADOR(A)</u></strong><strong><span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong>em<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span>atraso<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span>de<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span>1<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span>(um)<span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt;">&nbsp;</span>dia<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>com<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span>o<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span>pagamento<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>de qualquer<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>das<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>parcelas<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>n&atilde;o<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>poder&aacute;<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>ser<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>agraciado<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>no<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>sorteio,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>sendo<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>o<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>pr&ecirc;mio<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>destinado<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>ao<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>pr&oacute;ximo<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>sorteado,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>aferida<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-1.15pt;">&nbsp;</span>pontualidade ao<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>ﬁnal<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>do<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>dia<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>anterior<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>ao<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>sorteio,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span><strong><u><span style="letter-spacing:-0.15pt;">&Uacute;LTIMA</span></u></strong><strong><span style="letter-spacing:-1.45pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><u>TER&Ccedil;A-FEIRA</u></strong><strong><span style="letter-spacing:-1.45pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><u>DO</u></strong><strong><span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><u>M&Ecirc;S</u></strong>.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:12.5pt;"><strong>CL&Aacute;USULA D&Eacute;CIMA QUARTA</strong>: Para a consecu&ccedil;&atilde;o dos objetivos deﬁnidos na cl&aacute;usula D&eacute;cima <span style="letter-spacing:-0.15pt;">Segunda e D&eacute;cima Terceira,&nbsp;</span>o <strong><u>COMPRADOR(A)</u></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>sorteado receber&aacute;, imediatamente,<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>quita&ccedil;&atilde;o<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>integral<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>de<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">ste contrato</span>,<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>desonerado<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>e<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>eximido<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>do<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>pagamento<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>das<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>parcelas<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>vincendas,<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>e<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing:-0.25pt;">sem&nbsp;</span>nenhum<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>outro<span style="letter-spacing:-1.15pt;">&nbsp;</span>&ocirc;nus,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>taxa ou<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>despesa.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:12.5pt;"><strong>CL&Aacute;USULA D&Eacute;CIMA QUINTA</strong>: O sorteio ser&aacute; feito mensalmente, sempre na <strong><u><span style="letter-spacing:-0.15pt;">&Uacute;LTIMA&nbsp;</span></u></strong><strong><u>QUARTA-FEIRA</u></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>de cada m&ecirc;s, atrav&eacute;s da extra&ccedil;&atilde;o da <strong><u>LOTERIA FEDERAL</u></strong>, considerando-se a centena do primeiro pr&ecirc;mio. Cada <strong><u>COMPRADOR(A)</u></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>concorrer&aacute; com 4 (quatro) centenas, <strong><u>que lhes ser&atilde;o enviadas via e-mail e/ou SMS e/ou WhatsApp, ap&oacute;s o pagamento da primeira parcela e que passam a fazer parte integrante desse contrato</u></strong>.<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>Caso<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>n&atilde;o<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>haja<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>extra&ccedil;&atilde;o<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>da<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>Loteria<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>Federal<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>na<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>semana<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>(&uacute;ltima<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>quarta<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>do m&ecirc;s),<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>ser&aacute;<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>efetuada<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-1.15pt;">&nbsp;</span>premia&ccedil;&atilde;o<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>na<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>extra&ccedil;&atilde;o<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>seguinte.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:12.5pt;"><strong>CL&Aacute;USULA D&Eacute;CIMA SEXTA</strong>:<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span><strong><u>O</u></strong><strong><u><span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span></u></strong><strong><u>COMPRADOR(A)</u></strong><strong><span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong>receber&aacute;<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>o<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>pr&ecirc;mio<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>na<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>sede<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>da<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>empresa<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span><strong><u>VENDEDORA</u></strong><strong><span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong>(no<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>caso<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>de<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>retirada<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>do<span style="letter-spacing:-0.65pt;">&nbsp;</span>bem<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>f&iacute;sico),<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>ou<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>por<span style="letter-spacing:-0.6pt;">&nbsp;</span>meio digital,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>em<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>caso<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>de<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>pagamento<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>em<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>moeda,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>atrav&eacute;s<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>dos<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>meios<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>eletr&ocirc;nicos<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>de<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>pagamento<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>previamente<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>informados;</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:12.5pt;"><strong>CL&Aacute;USULA D&Eacute;CIMA S&Eacute;TIMA</strong>:<span style="letter-spacing:-1.15pt;">&nbsp;</span><strong><u>O</u></strong><strong><span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><u>COMPRADOR(A)</u></strong><strong><span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong>assume<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>as<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>afetas<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>&agrave;s<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>despesas<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>de<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>transfer&ecirc;ncia<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>de<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>propriedade,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>transporte<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>e<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>seguro<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>do<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>bem.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:12.5pt;"><strong>CL&Aacute;USULA D&Eacute;CIMA OITAVA</strong>:<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>Eventual<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>toler&acirc;ncia<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>por<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>parte<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>da<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span><strong><u>VENDEDORA</u></strong><strong><span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong>quanto<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>qualquer<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>das<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es<span style="letter-spacing:-0.25pt;">&nbsp;</span>contratuais<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>pactuadas<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>n&atilde;o<span style="letter-spacing:-0.3pt;">&nbsp;</span>caracterizar&aacute; ren&uacute;ncia ou remiss&atilde;o, ﬁcando restrita &agrave; altera&ccedil;&atilde;o pontual do detalhamento acertado, com sua validade condicionada ao <span style="letter-spacing:-0.2pt;">seu&nbsp;</span>termo.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:12.5pt;"><strong>CL&Aacute;USULA D&Eacute;CIMA NONA</strong>: As partes reconhecem que o presente contrato obedece rigorosamente a legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o consumerista, estando todos <span style="letter-spacing:-0.4pt;">os&nbsp;</span>contratantes revestidos de boa-f&eacute; objetiva e subjetiva, declarando o <strong><u>COMPRADOR(A)</u></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>ter lido e compreendido, na &iacute;ntegra, o presente<span style="letter-spacing:-0.4pt;">&nbsp;</span>contrato,<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>quanto<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>sua<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>extens&atilde;o<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>e<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>conte&uacute;do,<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>antes<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>de<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>ﬁrm&aacute;-lo,<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>ciente<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>que<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>a<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>presente<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>rela&ccedil;&atilde;o<span style="letter-spacing:-0.4pt;">&nbsp;</span>jur&iacute;dica<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>&eacute;<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span>de<span style="letter-spacing:-0.35pt;">&nbsp;</span><strong><u>COMPRA</u></strong><strong><span style="letter-spacing:-0.7pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><u>E VENDA ANTECIPADA</u></strong>, n&atilde;o se enquadrando nas legisla&ccedil;&otilde;es e regramentos espec&iacute;ﬁcos de CONS&Oacute;RCIO, SORTEIOS, CAPITALIZA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O<span style="letter-spacing:-1.15pt;">&nbsp;</span>PREMIADA,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>BINGOS,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>ETC,<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>que<span style="letter-spacing:-1.1pt;">&nbsp;</span>sabidamente<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>possuem<span style="letter-spacing:-1.05pt;">&nbsp;</span>regras<span style="letter-spacing:-1.15pt;">&nbsp;</span>pr&oacute;prias.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:12.5pt;"><strong>PAR&Aacute;GRAFO &Uacute;NICO</strong>: A <strong>VENDEDORA</strong> expressamente declara que a presente venda n&atilde;o depende de forma&ccedil;&atilde;o de grupos, por n&atilde;o se tratar de CONS&Oacute;RCIO ou qualquer modelo parecido de venda, sendo que a rela&ccedil;&atilde;o do <strong><u>COMPRADOR(A)</u></strong> com esta &eacute; exclusiva de compra e venda mercantil com pagamento antecipados de parcelas, com benef&iacute;cio oferecido pela manuten&ccedil;&atilde;o da pontualidade das parcelas. O benef&iacute;cio &eacute; direito do <strong><u>COMPRADOR(A)</u></strong> e obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o exclusiva da <strong>VENDEDORA</strong>, suportado por recursos pr&oacute;prios e independente da venda ou adimplento de eventuais outros clientes.</p>
